    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is flawless, with zero subframe fatigue and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior trim show no signs of UV degradation or mechanical wear. Documented rod bearing service and a pristine undercarriage make this a definitive investment-grade example for the serious collector.",
